<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Broom of Trilon Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Hail the Mistress of Air in the Temple of Solusek Ro to obtain the quest.<BR>
<BR>
2) Kill a Magician in Najena to obtain a broom.<BR>
<BR>
3) Kill a Griffon to obtain a Griffon Feather<BR>
<BR>
4) Kill a Cyclops to obtain a toe of a Cyclops<BR>
<BR>
5) Hand in the broom, feather, toe and a Star Ruby to obtain the Broom of Trilon.<BR>
<BR>
The broom is a focus object for a Magician to summon pet which is more powerful than the Magician could currently summon.  The focus object must be weilded (read: in one of your hands) for it to be used.  The Reclaim Energy effect is a seperate function.</div>
<BR>
